Hello, I found a problem with the app's UI design. When I started timing, I found a "RESET" widget in the upper right corner with an "hourglass" icon. If I only saw this "hourglass" icon, I might think it was used to set the time. But obviously it is used to reset time. The hourglass is slightly related to “RESET", which can easily mislead users. So, for better user experience, could you try to fix this issue?

